{"tid":2113544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關再多一人疑確診　北角海關總部大樓上班","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T09:48:15.000Z","uid":58867,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"930fd8c4fe2d9433d5828986eccf08b11be4b0b9","tid":2113544,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續爆發，據了解，今日(18日)再有一名海關關員確診，他隷屬海關版權及商標調查科版權及商標調查(行動)課，主要在北角海關總部大樓的23樓工作。據了解，在大樓23層工作的所有職員會進行深喉唾液檢測，並在家辦工直至檢測呈陰性，而有關地方亦會進行消毒。<br />\n據悉，在24至25樓工作的關員，亦可以在上司的指示下進行病毒檢測。本周三(15日)海關1名助理貿易管制主任初步確診新冠肺炎，該名人員於啟德工業貿易大樓20樓辦公，有關樓層不對外開放。<br />\n《香港疫慌》專頁: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/fea/hkdisease\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffea%2Fhkdisease&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c85ee4c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/fea/hkdisease</a>"},{"pid":"8ed1953ab27d3e73751f909261f226e54dd4eebf","tid":2113544,"uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"證明全部都係支那輸入 然後交叉感染<br />\n出完21萬免檢疫令出完奶共<br />\n惹到香港周圍都係 然後廣東限制入境<br />\n<br />\n香港封關話歧視 林鄭真係天下第一"},{"pid":"6e825b319539456be3ee2e78c11d1d6daf2e68bc","tid":2113544,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"聽做緊既朋友話應該唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385609f910f1f24d5be5c6297c21077a6dd5f074","tid":2113544,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"唔WFH唔怕"},{"pid":"b8782ea2f4a85ace34e57e6a362939b483e9a583","tid":2113544,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ed1953ab27d3e73751f909261f226e54dd4eebf","tid":2113544,"uid":123774,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"證明全部都係支那輸入 然後交叉感染<br />\n出完21萬免檢疫令出完奶共<